{"tid":2065944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：將嚴肅追究參與政治性罷工的公務員","createTime":"2020-06-16T02:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T03:51:43.000Z","uid":137088,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ab25cd6a2c448bf7986a61467a77702d960f403c","tid":2065944,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】多個工會及學生組織計劃發起的罷工罷課公投反對港區國安法，有份參與發起的 新公務員工會主席顏武周擔心，政府、港澳辦及中聯辦先後發表聲明譴責會阻嚇會員投票，他強調工會在公投無既定立場。<br />\n<br />\n公投由23個工會組成的聯合陣線及中學生行動籌備平台發起 ，工會日前表明，若公投有超過過半會員支持，將發起兩階段罷工。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，有關公務員組織在社交媒體表明參加的是反國安法罷工公投，採取政治性罷工手段，反對國家安全法，是公然違反公務員守則，政府定必嚴肅追究。"},{"pid":"56c3cb1ff1fa524eea05e165cf50c10905df8bec","tid":2065944,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb697a1047a9521975fb54134a032a3a8c78eb5","tid":2065944,"uid":214502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"中（國）立（場）"},{"pid":"7d860b7d91648c70c79f3e8d8a9043972215368e","tid":2065944,"uid":279298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得仲要追究埋有外國護照嘅公務員，佢哋叛國喎，效忠外國勢力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4eda8cc93bf6a2af1fdc5c7419150045691e89","tid":2065944,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"好大嘅官威呀包大人"},{"pid":"d6102371d01f12ad84b0640eec7d1afbbe1914b6","tid":2065944,"uid":300782,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed57289328159391e7a53a614e765fb0d1875c7","tid":2065944,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6102371d01f12ad84b0640eec7d1afbbe1914b6","tid":2065944,"uid":300782,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img